&lt;h2 id=&quot;domain-name&quot;&gt;Domain Name&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In this Internet-heavy age, every startup should ideally have its own domain name. This voting app is no exception.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Knowing that the “whowouldyouvote” handle was still available, I went ahead and acquired whowouldyouvote.com.&lt;/p&gt;

